datasets.name: dataset_22
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) AS `Daily Event Date`, `App Version` AS `App Version`, MEASURE(`Active Devices`) AS `Active Devices`, MEASURE(`Active Devices`) / SUM(MEASURE(`Active Devices`)) OVER (PARTITION BY `Event Date Time`) * 100 AS `% Active Devices` FROM `workspace.default.hpx_events_model` WHERE `Event Date Time` >= '2023-05-01' ORDER BY `Daily Event Date`

fields.name: % Active Devices
fields.expression: MEASURE(`Active Devices`) / SUM(MEASURE(`Active Devices`)) OVER (PARTITION BY `Event Date Time`) * 100
